CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 6, 1957, pg. 15 reads: "5. The natural Gas Companies' booth doubled in brass. They displayed the beautiful contest cakes on the final night, together with their complete line of gas appliances.  Representing are, left to right: Jams [sic] Griffin, Juanita Banks, Simon Lee Franklin, Harold Mason and Noraella Brown
TitMainTitle: James Griffin, Juanita Banks, Simon Lee Franklin, Harold Mason, and Noraella Brown posed in Natural Gas Companies booth in Syria Mosque for the 1957 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
